title: ADD_AUTHORIZED_PARACHUTE_MODEL
content:
0x8AC7AE9// AddAuthorizedParachuteModel
void ADD_AUTHORIZED_PARACHUTE_MODEL(int modelNameHash);Parameters:modelNameHash: Name hash of the model to allow to be used for the player ped's parachuteReturns: None.Adds the given model name hash to the list of valid models for the player ped's parachute.
